headline: Shopify, The Trade Desk, Wix, ZoomInfo, and Upstart Stocks Trade Up, What You Need To Know
summary: A number of stocks jumped in the afternoon session after positive news on corporate earnings, easing political and trade tensions, and optimism about future interest rate cuts all converged to lift investor sentiment.
